  "title": "$11/HR WAREHOUSE PACKER @ WOODLANDS📦",
  "description": "<p>🕒 Working Hours: Monday to Friday, 8:30 AM – 6:00 PM</p><p>💰 Pay: From $10/hour<br /></p><p>Why Join Us?</p><p>✅ Long-Term Career Opportunity</p><p>Start with a 3 month contract with early conversion to permanent for strong performers.</p><p>✅ Big Brand Experience</p><p>Gain hands-on experience in a fast-paced, team-oriented environment supporting a major company.</p><p>✅ Supportive Team Culture</p><p>Work alongside a reliable, friendly crew who value teamwork and efficiency.<br /></p><p>What You’ll Be Doing:</p><p> • Picking and packing of sportswear and related items</p><p> • Sorting, labeling, and preparing shipments</p><p> • Loading and unloading goods (up to 20KG)</p><p> • Assisting with general warehouse duties and ad-hoc tasks</p><p><br />What We’re Looking For:</p><p> • Warehouse experience required</p><p> • Able to handle up to 20KG</p><p> • Own safety shoes</p><p> • Punctual, reliable, and committed team player<br /></p><p>🎯 Ready to roll up your sleeves and join a growing team?</p><p>Apply now and take the next step in your logistics career!</p><p><br />📩 WHATSAPP wa.me/6589387313 TO APPLY🎊</p><p>Code: <strong>SPORTSWARE</strong></p><p>Full name:</p><p>Residential area:</p><p>Earliest availability date:</p><p>Commitment period:</p><p>Able to work on weekends?:</p><p>And please attached a copy of your resume💰 $11/hour</p><p>🕒 Mon – Fri | 8:30am – 5:45pm</p><p>📅 Long-term | Minimum 6 months commitment<br /></p><p>🛠 Job Scope</p><p>• Packing and repacking of goods</p><p>• General warehouse duties</p><p>• Sorting, labeling, and preparing items for dispatch</p><p>• Able to carry heavy items when required<br /></p><p>✅ Requirements</p><p>• Able to carry heavy loads up to 15 - 20kg</p><p>• Reliable and committed (long-term role)</p><p>• Comfortable working in a warehouse environment<br /></p><p>✨ Why Join?</p><p>• Stable working hours (office hours)</p><p>• Long-term opportunity</p><p>• Consistent weekday work<br /></p><p>How to Apply:</p><p>📞 WhatsApp: wa.me/6589387313<br /></p><p>Send with Code: <strong>WAREWOOD</strong> + these details:</p><p>✅ Full Name</p><p>✅ Residential Area</p><p>✅ Earliest Availability Date</p><p>✅ Commitment Period</p><p>✅ Able to work on weekends? (Y/N)</p><p>✅ Attach Resume</p><p><br /></p><p>Join these groups for more exciting job opportunities!</p><p>https://t.me/sgbesttempjobs</p><p>https://t.me/varioustempjobs</p><p><br /></p><p>Chia Xin Ee Crystal | R21103390</p><p>EA License No: 21C0626</p>",
